                                                 Karl Stratos
Deriving word embeddings
                                      stratos@cs.columbia.edu
_____________________________________________________________
Requirements: python (2.7), numpy, scipy, sparsesvd, matlab

Sanity: run "python debug.py" to ensure everything is working.

Usage: given a raw (but properly tokenized) text corpus. 
Using a toy corpus as example, run

(a) python cca.py --corpus input/example/example.corpus --cutoff 1
(b) python cca.py --stat input/example/example.cutoff1.window3/ --m 2 --kappa 2